Package: beforepaste
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: libx11-6, libxcb1, libxkbcommon0, libgtk-3-0, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Local clipboard protection for AI prompts
 BeforePaste watches AI paste targets and redacts API keys, tokens, private
 keys, and PII before they reach an AI prompt. It also includes an explicit
 trigger command for one-shot clipboard redaction.
